<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>68</hymn_number>
<title>Mungu Msaada Wetu TZR68</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Mungu msada wetu
 Tangu myaka yote,
 Ndiwe tumaini letu
 La zamani zote.

[V2]
 Kivuli cha kiti chako
 Ndiyo ngome yetu.
 Watosha mkono wako
 Ni ulinzi wetu.

[V3]
 Kwanza havijakuwako
 Nchi na milima,
 Ndiwe Mungu; chini yako
 Twakaa salama.

[V4]
 Na myaka elfu ni kama
 Siku moja kwako;
 Utanilinda daima
 Tu wenyeji wako.

[V5]
 Binadamu huondoka,
 Mwisho hana kitu;
 Kama ndoto hutoweka
 Ndivyo hali yetu.

[V6]
 Ila wewe Mungu wetu
 Ndiwe wa kudumu;
 Ndiwe bora, ngome yetu
 Twakaa dawamu.</lyrics>
</song>